:: Tome

[[Tome|https://tome.sibr.dev/]] shows the results of each player's at bat and basic pitcher performance stats (e.g. number of strikeouts) in a given game. Brought to you by iliana and ch00beh. New features are in progress, to make this a tool for broadcasters.

Source code [[here|https://github.com/Society-for-Internet-Blaseball-Research/tome]]. Discussion at @@.channel;#ch00bs-cursed-projects@@ in 'Major Projects'.